text.tspan: The avatars show the dominant
style from Instagram in different
cities at a time.
Clicking on the avatar also selects the city for
the side view. The first city that you choose
will be regarded as primary one, and you can
compare it with any other city in the side
view by clicking on other avatars.
You can sort the cities
by different styles.
Hover on the avatar to see
details of the citys majority
clothing style and accessories.
HOW TO USE V-STYLE
Click on a certain city to see
which cities have the most
similar style at that time.
Trend tab
will show a line chart where you can compare
the trends on a single style element between the two cities.
Combo tab
will show a correlation matrix of the cities
different combo styles, with the color showing the
dominant color of that combo, and the saturation showing
its prevelance. Clicking on a cell shows the corresponding
Instagram pictures.
Drag or click on the timeline
to change the season that you
want to explore.
